SitesWrapper-GAE-GWT

Packages 
Package Description
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.client
SitesWrapper Application Presentation Layer Network is a state of the art platform and network independent presentation system which leverages the entire spectrum of Google technologies to manage information and business process in order to provide management, the workforce and customers what they need to make and implement decisions easily, efficiently and effectively.
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.endpoints
Contains the endpoints enabling web service CRUD of the Application Data Model
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.event
Contains classes which manage events and the event bus
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.factory
Contains factory interfaces and concrete classes.
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.model
Contains the Application Data Model
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.presenter
Contains interfaces and classes which handle the Presenter in the MVP pattern.
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.resources
Contains html and other resources
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.server
Contains the Server Service Wrapper components of SitesWrapper.
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.shared
Contains SitesWrapper components shared between the Server Service Wrapper and the Client Wrapper.
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.utilities
Contains utility classes
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.view
Contains classes which implement Views in the MVP pattern
com.urlisit.siteswrapper.cloud.widgets
